  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_144",
    "english": "A wizard who made a contract with an interdimensional being, allowing them to use supernatural powers. Even if they're borrowing those powers, they can manipulate them with skill based on their understanding and knowledge of them, and can not only attack, but dispel the enemy's magic as well.",
